ugh less clear) for\nlinear clustering in the real peculiar velocity data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2011 19:56:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Sep 2012 16:35:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
